sources.description: Episode 11 of the syndicated filmed series. Captain Z-ro uses his time machine to protect humankind at various junctions in history. Public domain status: Registered as a published film 14 Jan 55 (LP11100). No renewed. Subsequent copyright re-registration rejected in 1985: Captain Z-Ro/Attila the Hun.
